name: Л
description:
NFT in 5 years.

I'm not going to pretend to have a good understanding and understanding of the subject of what it is and make assumptions about how it will evolve in 5-10 years. That would be dishonest and a bit hypocritical. Things are moving so inexorably fast with technology these days... but I know for a fact that I wanted my letter to be included in this project too! I'm always in favor of development and always for experimentation, switching from one tool to another and breadth of vision, so I hope to be able to "hop on that train of the future" too.
